01:09:26.319 --> 01:09:45.319
Because we use statistical forecasting, we were using it, I was going to say, as more of a benchmark for our commercial partners. There wasn't a lot of compliance present out pharma, especially Opiates, which is one of the products that Mallinckrodt makes. It's very highly regulated, as you know.

01:09:45.319 --> 01:10:12.319
