01:16:42.319 --> 01:17:06.319
In generics, we cannot do promotion. So, we can't say, hey, we got a hydro promotion going on. Obviously, the EA would not like us if we did that. So, in that kind of industry, like a consumer packaged goods perhaps or something, you could – if you had a forecast when it was going to happen and then maybe a past time series of that, you would want to put that as an explanatory variable in your model.

01:17:07.319 --> 01:17:16.319
