01:20:16.319 --> 01:20:37.319
So it's a mixed integer linear program for those who are familiar with operations research terminology. Essentially, you just – the OMPR package builds the model based upon your parameters and then sends it to a solver, and solvers – a lot of people – dedicated people work in those, but essentially, it uses a lot of different approaches to solving the problem and picks the best one essentially.

